00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:26.640
in the Atlantic titled,
A Nice Gershwin Tune."

00:08:26.640 --> 00:08:30.560
Within this essay, he declares
that Rhapsody in Blue is

00:08:30.560 --> 00:08:32.860
