had already written.

00:18:30.670 --> 00:18:33.290
But for some reason no one seems
to ever question this aspect

00:18:33.290 --> 00:18:36.490
of the Rhapsody's creation
story until now.

00:18:36.490 --> 00:18:39.570
One story that has been told about
the creation of the Rhapsody time

00:18:39.570 --> 00:18:42.440
and time again is that
George Gershwin had forgotten

00:18:42.440 --> 00:18:44.720
about his commission from
the Paul Whiteman Orchestra

00:18:44.720 --> 00:18:47.870
until his older brother Ira
