00:18:47.870 --> 00:18:50.590
about the supposed jazz concerto
that Gershwin was writing

00:18:50.590 --> 00:18:56.740
in a New York Herald Tribune
article on January 4, 1924.

00:18:56.740 --> 00:18:59.540
Now this article on January 4
apparently spurned George Gershwin

00:18:59.540 --> 00:19:01.210
