slightly less than four weeks

00:19:22.470 --> 00:19:26.990
to compose Rhapsody in Blue
once pen was put to paper.

00:19:26.990 --> 00:19:28.350
The ink manuscript, however,

00:19:28.350 --> 00:19:32.160
suggests an even more
compressed compositional timeline.

00:19:35.860 --> 00:19:39.820 position:56%
The first grouping of ink manuscript
