00:19:43.270 --> 00:19:46.370
until just before the start
of the first piano cadenza.

00:19:46.370 --> 00:19:49.860
Although many that are here tonight
are familiar with the Rhapsody,

00:19:49.860 --> 00:19:51.350
here's what this first
grouping sounds

00:19:51.350 --> 00:19:54.040
like in it's original
1924 arrangement.

00:19:54.040 --> 00:19:56.000
It's a very different
sound world than that

00:19:56.000 --> 00:19:59.120
of the more ubiquitous
symphonic arrangement.

