00:21:23.700 --> 00:21:26.260
Now, if we look at
Gershwin's pencil score,

00:21:26.260 --> 00:21:28.910
we see that this opening
passage is the most fully flushed

00:21:28.910 --> 00:21:30.890
out of the entire manuscript.

00:21:30.890 --> 00:21:33.900
There are instrumental assignments
for the melody, articulation

00:21:33.900 --> 00:21:35.290
and accent markings throughout

00:21:35.290 --> 00:21:38.490
and dynamic specified
