00:21:45.680 --> 00:21:47.880
in the -- I'm sorry, only
employed the jazz band

00:21:47.880 --> 00:21:49.690
in the first three systems.

00:21:49.690 --> 00:21:52.770
Such care suggests
greater attention paid

00:21:52.770 --> 00:21:56.570
